{"tid":1962401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[韓國瑜準備玩撚完]罷免高雄市長韓國瑜連署達門檻","createTime":"2020-04-07T12:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T12:36:26.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82ec8c9050419e07dc72510df8d5467a92c2836b","tid":1962401,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:33:31.000Z","msg":"高雄市選委會召開委員會議，審查通過罷免市長韓國瑜第二階段連署書。<br />\n<br />\n主委陳雄文表示，罷免連署書剔除重複或資料不全，有效份數超過37萬，達罷免門檻。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市選委會整理資料名冊後，明天將名冊送交中選會。中選會若核實聯署人數，罷免案將會成立，屆時會由高雄市議會定出投票日期，一般估計在6月中。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519394-20200407.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519394-20200407.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYkwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=9a6a49fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519394-20200407.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a4308844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519394-20200407.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d0a752459af48eeb7b67732ae4347fc7befa8095","tid":1962401,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJQ7ANN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJQ7ANN.jpg&h=5bc3abe2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a84ee2f15cef2291a00c25951d25d4c2024e57de","tid":1962401,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82ec8c9050419e07dc72510df8d5467a92c2836b","tid":1962401,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:33:31.000Z","msg":"高雄市選委會召開委員會議，審查通過罷免市長韓國瑜第二階段連署書。<br />\n<br />\n主委陳雄文表示，罷免連署書剔除重複或資料不全，有效份數超過37萬，達罷免門檻。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市選委會整理資料名冊後，明天將名冊送交中選會。中選會若核實聯署人數，罷免案將會成立，屆時會由高雄市議會定出投票日期，一般估計在6月中。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519394-20200407.ht